---
// src/components/RealityCheck.astro
---

<section class="py-32 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800" id="timeline">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-6">
        Real Talk: This is an <span class="text-blue-400">Investment</span>,<br> not a Lottery Ticket.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Most agencies promise overnight magic. We prefer to tell you the truth. 
        Here is exactly what the first few months look like.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-24">
      
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-800 via-blue-900/50 to-emerald-900/50 -z-10 transform translate-y-4"></div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700 relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col">
        <div class="p-8 flex-grow relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-300 font-bold text-xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-white group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors relative z-10 border border-slate-600 group-hover:border-white">1</div>
            
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Month 1</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Building The Engine</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    We build the site, write the words, and connect you to Google Maps. It's hard work. We are laying the bricks for your digital storefront.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 border-t border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-200 font-medium">
                <i data-lucide="minus" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500"></i>
                <span>Silence. (This is normal).</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700 relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col">
        <div class="p-8 flex-grow relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 font-bold text-xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors relative z-10 border border-blue-800 group-hover:border-blue-500">2</div>
            
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400">Month 2-3</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Earning Trust</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Google finds your site but doesn't trust you yet. They check: "Is this a real business?" They send a trickle of visitors just to test you out.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 border-t border-slate-700 bg-blue-900/20">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-200 font-medium">
                <i data-lucide="search" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400"></i>
                <span>You appear in search results.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/50 border border-slate-700 relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col">
        <div class="p-8 flex-grow relative z-10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold text-xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors relative z-10 border border-emerald-800 group-hover:border-emerald-500">3</div>
            
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">Month 4+</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Floodgates Open</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    You passed the test. Google now trusts you enough to show your business to people all over the city, not just your street.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 border-t border-slate-700 bg-emerald-900/20">
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What you see</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-200 font-medium">
                <i data-lucide="phone-call" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400"></i>
                <span>Your phone rings. A lot.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center border-t border-slate-800 pt-20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-normal">
            "If you need customers <span class="text-slate-500 line-through decoration-slate-600">tomorrow</span>, run ads. It's faster.<br class="hidden md:block" />
            If you want customers <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold border-b-2 border-blue-400 pb-0.5">forever</span> without paying per click, build this."
        </h3>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>